name: 利奥·弗朗尼希
name_full: 利奥·弗朗尼希 Leo Franich
introduction: Leo is the son of actress Megan Franich and brother to actor Sam Franich. He was born in Los Angeles and also has New Zealand citizenship through his NZ born parents. He started acting and modeling at a young age and has been in campaigns for Louis Vuitton, Texas Tourism and Joel Osteen to name but a few. In 2022 he got to show his film acting chops alongside Zac Efron and Lily James playing their children in The Iron Claw alongside his brother Sam.
